Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

Here's presenting "CUSTODY" the Hindi Dubbed Version of the Telugu action thriller Film "CUSTODY", starring Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Anandhi, R. Sarath Kumar, Jiiva and Sampath Raj in lead roles.    

Movie (Hindi Dubbed):- Custody 
Original Movie Name:- Custody in Telugu 
StarCast:- Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Jiiva, R. Sarath Kumar, Sampath Raj, Anandhi
Music:- Yuvan Shankar Raja, Ilaiyaraaja 
Producer:- Srinivasaa Chituri 
Director:- Venkat Prabhu 

Constable Shiva is assigned to escort a witness from police custody to the courtroom. However, he soon learns Shiva that the entire police department wants the witness dead.

#nagachaitanya #actionmovie #custodymovie

Bhairabi is a Web series with a mixture of social, family and divine powers. In this web series, the topic of how a family can become disturbed despite being a divine power is tried to be raised.

The snakes and Gods used in it are created by graphics. It does not aim to promote any religion, sect or caste and spread falsehood. The aim of this web series is to entertain the audience with only positive messages and innovative use of graphics.
